Hmm...havent updated in like...4ever...lets c...last time was..November 25? hmm...lol...well...lets c...Dec. 4 i was in the trenton parade...it was fricken freezing! lol...the next say was the rochester hills parade..fun fun...I was on tv! the camera was actually on me...o god..how horrible...lol...Dec.6 was our christmas concert...blah...it went good i guess...the next day i started drivers trainin...the most borin class on the face of the earth..ughh..lol...i was happy when that ended on christmas eve! lol...speakin of which..christmas eve i went to my grandmas for dinner w/ my dads side of the family...that was fun..lol...had a good christmas...got a new tv, dvd player, quite a few games (board games,computer games,playstaion and game cube games), a couple Michigan sweaters michigan pajama pants (GO BLUE! lol), dvd's,a red wings blanket (so warm and comfortable...lol), uhh...CD's, gift cards, a couple puzzles, and sum other small stuff 2...on christmas we had dinner w/ my mas side of the family...New Years was kinda borin...did nuthin this year..every new year is the same...just another year....Christmas break was awesome...i never wanted to go bak to school...im also very sick of every1 there....ive come to find that i have only 1 or 2 GOOD friends...all the rest r just like every1 else...uhh...got my Permit January 3...i love it...lol...school has been borin..but wat else is new....uhh...Solo and Ensamble in a couple weeks...geez we need 2 really practice...well...thats about it...

 

ill update again eventually...mayb..hah...lol..

7:05 pm

hey every1! the past couple of days have been ok i guess....neway...saturday was our last competition in like white lake michigan or sumthin and it was freezing and raining...almost the whole time : ( neway we got 12/12 but thats ok b/c we did break 50 (50.6) which means we get to shave mr.d's head! YAY!! lol....b/c it was rainin we were aloud 2 stay inside..which meant we had like a long time...me and becca went around the school and explored it and we went outside and walked around and bought buttons...lol..they said....Flute....football fields were made for marching bands....the football team will be playing before and after the premier performance of the marching band....and...marching band is all i do....ya...today was BORING....!!!!! i havent felt well all day cause of stupid marching band bein outside in the coldand i have 2 tests 2morrow one of which i did not study 4 b/c i was 2 busy studying 4 geometry which i dont understand.........errrrrrrr.......well thats it...lol........ill update next time i think about it.......

i had a nice long entry typed but then my computer decided 2 be idiodic and freeze up...grr...lol....sooo....heres a shorter version...lol...Band Camp.....it was fun i guess...i wanted 2 come home b/c i was homesick but otherwise i liked it...the cabins were nice...normal water,showers,bathrooms...Yay...lol...i was really home sick tho...i cried like evry night but no1 knew b/c i dont like 2 show my feelings...*sigh* i dont wanna get on other peoples nerves w/ my problems...*sigh* however Kelly Stonebreaker and Jessica really helped me b/c there was a time during an activity where they noticed i wasnt very happy soo they came and talked 2 me and cheered me up...they were really nice...it made me fell soo much better! neway...well we got up, ate, morning stretches, drill,lunch,sectionals, full band at frontier, dinner, drill, evening activity, bed.....bascially r day everyday...lol...i was soo happy saturday 2 c my mom and dad....the show turned out pretty good....we didnt march it all b/c it stormed wednesday and friday night soo it took practice time away and we werent ready 4 the end of the show....we did really good considerin it was r 1st performance..all the freshman did soo well ud think they were 2nd year marchers...lol...every1 should come c our show atleast once....itll be great!!

i decided i like 2 new people! **** and ***  One of them sat w/ us freshman at dinner even tho he didnt have 2 and talked 2 us and made it a point 2 get 2 no us (it was me becca stephani and hilary)...and i thought that was really nice....the other 1 also sat w/ us at dinner when he didnt have 2...and hes  like pretty popular and all the juniors decided 2 sit 2gether and they had a seat 4 him and everything but he came and sat w/ us instead and he made the people that wanted 2 sit w/ him move and come sit w/ us..how sweet...lol...he was halarious...u couldnt take 1 bite of food w/o like chokin on it b/c he was constantly sayin sumthin funny....lol...heh..those 2 days made me happier and made me feel better....too bad theyre both juniors...*sigh* i guess ill get over it just like i always have 2 cause nuthin ever goes my way...*sigh*

u feel soo proud on the field especially in uniform...last year i thought Marching band would be dumb but i no better now! I love it...bein able 2 represent the school...*sigh*such a great feelin!

Band geek and proud!!! lol   : P

PLEASE PLEASE PLEASE comment...grrr...no1 ever does nad it aggrivates me....lol...PLEASE!!!

well....2day i had 2 get up early and go to a flute sectional at 10...it was a blast! we all sat around 4 like 10 minutes and then decided we wanted 2 go 2 mcdonalds so 7 of us including Rachel (the driver/sectional leader) got in her Neon and went....lol....it was very corwded....there were 5 of us in the backseat (a 3 person seat) lol....it was a blast tho....we all just like sat at mcdonalds 4 like 2 hours and talked and laughed...and omg...this guy walked in mcdonalds and Danni thought he was hot so she went up him while he was in line and she goes "excuse me..but i just wanted u 2 no i think ur really hot" we all laughed at her 4 a good 10 minutes or longer....this season is gonna be soo much fun! then b/c we had a woodwind sectional at 1pm we all decded 2 hang around the school until then....the woodwind sectional was BORING!!! They always r! i hate goin 2 woodwind sectionals...and its 3 hours long (1-4) then he always lets out out like 10 minutes late! so i had just enough time 2 run home and eat and go online 4 like 10 minutes and then i had 2 leave so i could be like 10 minutes early for my full band pracice at 5:30-8:30 (as he says....2 be early is 2 be on time to b on time is 2 be late and 2 be late is 2 be forgotten.....how stupid!!!) I cant stand mr. d...he is sooo confusing...hes constantly changing things and bein really stupid....haha....he got locked in mrs day's office in the band room at the woodwind sectional (i wish he wouldnt of been able 2 get out...lol).The full band was at Roosevelt on the back practice field b/c they were scrimmagin on the main football field...all we did was set drill and practice marching...grrr...i couldnt get the box march i kept wantin 2 go the wrong way and it was really confusin but does he help? no...he said i wasnt listenin...grr.....im a first year marcher i mean come on....i think i have the right 2 be confused cause we like just learned it! o well...neway after the full band we all piled in Rachel's car again and went 2 tye dye our sections flute shirts and socks....were goin back 2 her house 2morrow 2 finish them cause they had 2 dry and it was like 11 when we got done dyin them....that little get 2gether was also a blast.....we ate pizza and talked and just had a lotta fun! i love the flute section! we all get along soo well! neway were gonna do the same 2morrow...get 2gether at her house 2 finish everything up and work on sum music be4 band camp....which o leave 4 on Sunday by the way so dont 4get 2 tell me bye bye! lol...

hmmm....last night i didnt update cause i was lazy and angry and upset and mad! ok first of all i had a lot on my mind...i didnt wanna go 2 the woodwind sectional 2day b/c i was afraid he was gonna try and make us sing alone...which i refuse 2 do....then i was thinkin about how much i liked *him* and i have no clu weather he nos or not b/c my friends r whacked out and the lie and i cant trust them and theyd do sumthin like tell him...not Kate tho...b/c i can trust her....she would never do that 2 me...i can tell her nething! shes like my best friend...lol...and i was especially mad b/c my sn got hacked and they changed my password and now i cant get on my like favorite sn.....and i cant find the paper in which i had all my bl written down on....Grr.....then i was thinkin about band camp and how i didnt wanna goo..really i  dont but i have 2 in order 2 be in marching band and i dont wanna drop marching band cause i like my section and the uniforms! lol....so between *him* and band camp and the woodwind sectional and my sn gettin hacked it created a lot of anger and unhappiness in me that i couldnt let out b/c it was really late and there was no1 to yell at and blah blah........neway enough about that junk....im gonna quit typin now cause im gettin lazy...lol....ill update 2morrow and saturday and then the followin saturday after i get home from band camp....ill let yall no how that went! well

hey every1! well...2day was mostly BAND...yippee...lol...I had a woodwind sectional from 1-4. That was like really borin...we learned this choral or sumthin like that and Mr. and Mrs. D. tried 2 make me sing! alone at that! NO WAY...hahaha...first off i cant carry a tune...lol....secondly...if I wanted 2 sing i wouldve joined choir..not band! neway he says he can sit there and stare at u all day till u sing so if thats the case i guess he'll be starin at me an awful long time b/c i WILL NOT sing! I hate it...i didnt even sing in elementary during music...lol...singing is just not sumthin i like 2 do...so he can get over it! haha...lol....then i had just enough time 2 get sumthin 2 eat and relax a lil then i had 2 go back again for a 5:30-8:30 at Roosevelt. That sectional was really actually kinda fun...we marched forward, backward and then we learned 2 march sideways both ways and then we put it all 2gether to do wat the call sumthin like a box march where u well...march in a box form...i think its sumthin like foward 8 . .sideways left 8...backwards 8 and sideways right...i think...not positive tho...i was Extremely confused...but im sure ill get the hang of it!Im determined 2! lol. I think it was fun and it felt really good when i did it exactly right (which wasnt very often...lol). The last hour we worked on part of the pregame drill. Its really cool b/c we form like a W for wyandotte of course and i heard we might be tryin a formation of RHS....that would be cool....we learned wat yard line we should be at or how many steps we should be to the left of the sideline and how many steps in front of or behind the hashmarks we should be. It sounds confusin if ur not in band but its actually pretty easy...but dont get me wrong...i was extremely confused 2day...lol...well...now that fun and ive told u all about it...im gonna go b/c im tired of typin! lol...Thursday i have band like ALL day...fun fun! 10-12 flute sectional...1-4 woodwind sectional...and 5:30-8:30 full band marching again...yay...lol...after the full band the flutes r goin over Rachels (our section leader) house 2 tye dye r shirts and mayb socks i guess...Wat an exciting day...well....i guess ill update again 2morrow unless sumthin funny or exciting happens from now till i go 2 bed...
